# Story 8.1: Unified Design Tokens

## Story Metadata
- **Epic:** 8 - Visual Redesign & Canvas Migration
- **Story ID:** 8-1-unified-design-tokens
- **Status:** ready-for-dev
- **Priority:** P0
- **Persona:** Developer
- **Added:** SCP-001 (2025-12-28)

## User Story
As a **Developer**,
I want **a single source of truth for colors and spacing**,
So that **all components are visually consistent**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status | Visual Verification |
|----|----------|--------|---------------------|
| AC1 | CSS variables defined in globals.css | PENDING | Code review required |
| AC2 | Tailwind config uses same palette | PENDING | |
| AC3 | All components use tokens, not hardcoded colors | PENDING | |
| AC4 | Design token documentation created | PENDING | |
| AC5 | All pages pass visual consistency check | PENDING | Playwright screenshots all pages |

## Technical Requirements

### CSS Variables (globals.css)
```css
:root {
  /* Background Colors */
  --bg-primary: #0A0A0A;      /* Main background */
  --bg-secondary: #141414;    /* Card/panel background */
  --bg-tertiary: #1E1E1E;     /* Elevated surfaces */
  --bg-hover: #252525;        /* Hover states */

  /* Text Colors */
  --text-primary: #FFFFFF;    /* Primary text */
  --text-secondary: #A1A1A1;  /* Secondary text */
  --text-muted: #6B6B6B;      /* Muted/disabled text */

  /* Brand Colors */
  --accent-primary: #3B82F6;  /* Primary actions (blue-500) */
  --accent-success: #22C55E;  /* Success states (green-500) */
  --accent-warning: #F59E0B;  /* Warning states (amber-500) */
  --accent-error: #EF4444;    /* Error states (red-500) */

  /* Maintenance Type Colors */
  --maint-pm1: #3B82F6;       /* PM1 - blue-500 */
  --maint-pm2: #7C3AED;       /* PM2 - violet-600 */
  --maint-hm: #F59E0B;        /* HM - amber-500 */
  --maint-ovh: #EF4444;       /* OVH - red-500 */

  /* Borders */
  --border-default: #2A2A2A;
  --border-hover: #3A3A3A;

  /* Spacing (consistent 4px grid) */
  --space-xs: 4px;
  --space-sm: 8px;
  --space-md: 16px;
  --space-lg: 24px;
  --space-xl: 32px;
  --space-2xl: 48px;

  /* Border Radius */
  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
  --radius-full: 9999px;
}
```

### Tailwind Config Updates
```typescript
